Here are paste-ready photorealistic prompts you can use in Nano Banana (or similar image models). Pick one scene or mix details from two prompts.

Banking
Prompt:
Photorealistic retail banking branch interior at midday, warm wood and frosted glass dividers, small queue stanchions, customer and teller in profile at a counter (transaction screens and forms blurred and unreadable), potted plants and subtle architectural detail, natural light from street-facing windows mixed with recessed ceiling banks, candid documentary framing, no bank name on walls, no logos, no cash-count hero shot, no faces toward camera.

Shot on full-frame DSLR, 85mm or 35mm, f/5.6–f/8 for clarity, Adobe neutral profile, minimal oversharpening, natural chromatic aberration, real-world imperfections, documentary editorial style.


